{"type": "article", "id": 19934, "title": "带粗圆指针的挂钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-30T07:20:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060614065731KO7gte2YqlnIhH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这面挂钟没有任何刻度指示，只有单色表盘和粗圆的指针。通过颜色的对比区别，有简约的时尚感。瑞典设计师 Jonas Wagell 从前是学平面设计和排版的，因寻找不到简单而有图象感的挂钟，所以自己设计了一个。它改变了人们对精细钟表的固有观念，同时显得很轻盈，适合年轻人。挂钟由丹麦家具品牌 Normann Copenhagen 生产，预计下个月上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150255MYTGqWL4x3vkpslU.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150255dFpYGtnIOhUScglE.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261502569Y0SWo1AtpvKDkf3.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150256ouz9cOU7hFwkYfqs.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1089\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.16346154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}